        "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\n> Patch Set 1:\n> \n> Thanks james for the review, Inter layer lock ID, used for path computation in a topology covering multiple layers, its required to associate overlay topology TP to underlay topolofy TTP,relationship between overlay TP to underlay TTP will be added during topology  discovery based on interlayer lock id.\n\nThanks, but what is the source of the Interlayer Lock ID?  is it stored in a separate vertex or is it external to AAI?",
